title: Pitchfork's Top 50 Albums for 2008 (46-50) + 10 Bonus Albums
description:
This is my last (4th) torrent, from a 4 torrent set - each set in 15 album sets of Pitchfork's Top 50 Albums of 2008. This set includes an additional 10 albums that are some of my favorite one for 2008 that were not part of the original top 50. I also included my end of 2008 Playlist. Here is 46-50:

46. Beach House - Devotion
47. The Tallest Man On Earth - Shallow Graves 
48. High Places - High Places 
49. Crystal Stilts - Alight Of Night
50. Ponytail - Ice Cream Spiritual

These are my favorite additional 10 albums that were not part of Pitchfork's list: as well as my end of 2008 playlist:

Amadou & Mariam - Welcome To Mali
Animal Collective - Merriweather Post Pavilion - LIVE
Bon Iver - For Emma, Forever Ago 
Dodos - The Visitor
Dosh - Wolves and Wishes 
Dub Colossus - In A Town Called Addis
El Guincho - Alegranza
Steinski - What Does It All Mean- 1983-2006 Retrospective-2CD
StevieLee's End of 2008 Playlist
Sun Kil Moon - April 
The Matthew Herbert Big Band - There's Me And There's You

I sincerely want to thank everyone here in TPBcommunity for making this one of the best torrent sites anywhere. May you all have a peaceful, prosperous and transformational 2009. TIME2WAKEUP indeed...Cheers!
